Introduction

Infrastructure as code
Automation of your Infrastructure
Keep your infrastructure in a certain state


 2 web instances with 2 volumes and load balancer
 suppose if 1 is delete then terraform will create
 Make your infrastructure auditable
Ansible, chef helps with installation and configuration 

Terraform automates the infrastructure itself 


