terraform console
> var.myvar
"hello world"
> exit

*******************
terraform commands

terraform plan - Testing what infrastructure would be built based on our terraform files
terraform plan -out changes.terraform : Keeping the changes in an out file
terraform apply changes.terraform : apply terraform changes
terraform destroy: Afterwards the infrastructure can be destroyed.



